  "rationale": "<p>Choice B is correct. The number that is 17 less than n is (n &minus; 17). Their product is n(n &minus; 17) = n<sup>2</sup> &minus; 17n.</p><p>Choice A adds 17 instead of subtracting. Choices C and D include extraneous constant terms not present in the product.</p>",
